## Use the space below to document your plan for implementing CS Discoveries. 

#### Consider the following when making your plan:

* Which units will you include in your course? 
* Which unit will you start with? 
* Will you teach full units, or one chapter from multiple units? 
* When will you teach each unit that you have selected? 
* Will you teach different units across grade levels? If yes, which content will you include in each grade level course?

